export const text = `<Button>click</Button>
<Button size="sm" color="#AB47BC">
  click
</Button>
<Button size="md" color="#EF5350">
  click
</Button>
<Button size="lg">click</Button>
<Button size="md" disabled={true}>
  click
</Button>`;
